Text:
Hello again 

Can you please upload The Paino handbook by Carl Humphries ?

Thank you.

It's amazing that the author's studies conclude that fish do feel pain, she took the trouble to write a whole book about it, and yet is still "far from anti-fishing". Many meat/fish-eaters choose to ignore the details of animal suffering, but for one who knows all about the matter, to choose to disregard it is doubly disturbing.
